node.text:
From the dual headlights, to the coves, to the grill, to the distinct tail lights, the #C1 has a lot of style to offer. What’s your favorite design element about the first generation Corvette? 🇺🇸 
#SWIPE for more photos
1958 Chevrolet Corvette that is available in black with silver coves with a black interior.
Features: 4-speed manual transmission, 283 V8 engine, steel wheels, knock-off hubcaps, hard top, and white wall tires. An original California car that has some checking in the paint. 
✅ This American classic is available for $67,500
Please include your name|email and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

node.text:
#FERRARIFRIDAY
Fun Ferrari Fact:
The 328 has been described as one of the most usable classic Ferraris because of its durable road record, history of appreciating value, and classical aesthetics! 💚
Featured here is a 1986 Ferrari 328GTS in an extremely desirable and sought-after factory color combination of Verde Scuro Metallic (color code #603/C) with a chocolate interior.
- 58,144 miles on the odometer
- Clean Carfax
Key Features: 5-speed manual transmission, air conditioning, power windows, 4-wheel disc brakes, jack, and tool kit. 
✅ A gorgeous color combination Ferrari that is ready to be driven and enjoyed. Do not miss your chance to jump into the ownership of this amazing Italian sports car that is available for $89,950
Please include your name|email and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

node.text:
#DidYouKnow The ‘T’ stands for Touring and was first applied to the 1968 911T! 💚
This amazing and highly collectible 1971 Porsche 911T Targa featured with matching numbers is available in its factory color combination of Green Metallic with a black interior.
Key Features: 4-speed manual transmission, Weber carburetors, headrest, chrome rocker panels, leather-wrapped steering wheel,
4-wheel disc brakes, Fuchs wheels, jack, and spare tire. Also included with this vehicle are service documents and receipts dating
from 1980 to 2013 totaling over $11,000. A very clean and presentable 911T Targa that is available for $76,500
Please include your name|email and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.
